---
import PageShell from '../../components/PageShell.astro';
import CTABox from '../../components/CTABox.astro';
import ComparisonTable from '../../components/ComparisonTable.astro';

const tocItems = [
  { id: 'overview', text: 'Overview', level: 2 },
  { id: 'coverage-comparison', text: 'Coverage Comparison', level: 2 },
  { id: 'pricing', text: 'Pricing', level: 2 },
  { id: 'network-and-claims', text: 'Network and Claims', level: 2 },
  { id: 'who-should-choose', text: 'Who Should Choose Which', level: 2 },
  { id: 'verdict', text: 'Our Verdict', level: 2 },
];

const relatedLinks = [
  { title: 'BUPA Global Review', href: '/providers/bupa-global' },
  { title: 'GeoBlue Review', href: '/providers/geoblue' },
  { title: 'Best US Expat Insurance', href: '/best/us-expat-insurance' },
];

const coverageColumns = [
  { key: 'feature', header: 'Feature' },
  { key: 'bupa', header: 'BUPA Global' },
  { key: 'geoblue', header: 'GeoBlue' },
];

const coverageRows = [
  { feature: 'Inpatient Care', bupa: true, geoblue: true },
  { feature: 'Outpatient Care', bupa: true, geoblue: true },
  { feature: 'Mental Health', bupa: 'Better than average', geoblue: 'Moderate' },
  { feature: 'Maternity', bupa: '10-12 mo wait', geoblue: '12 mo wait' },
  { feature: 'Dental', bupa: 'Optional', geoblue: 'Optional' },
  { feature: 'Telemedicine', bupa: true, geoblue: true },
  { feature: 'Medical Evacuation', bupa: true, geoblue: true },
  { feature: 'US Coverage', bupa: 'Add-on', geoblue: 'Included (BCBS network)' },
  { feature: 'Non-US Citizens', bupa: 'Yes', geoblue: 'Limited' },
];

const pricingColumns = [
  { key: 'age', header: 'Age' },
  { key: 'bupa', header: 'BUPA Global' },
  { key: 'geoblue', header: 'GeoBlue' },
];

const pricingRows = [
  { age: '30', bupa: '$170-260/mo', geoblue: '$150-230/mo' },
  { age: '40', bupa: '$230-350/mo', geoblue: '$200-310/mo' },
  { age: '50', bupa: '$300-460/mo', geoblue: '$280-430/mo' },
  { age: '60', bupa: '$450-680/mo', geoblue: '$400-620/mo' },
];
---

<PageShell
  title="BUPA Global vs GeoBlue"
  description="Compare BUPA Global and GeoBlue international health insurance. Premium service vs BCBS network access for expats."
  headline="BUPA Global vs GeoBlue"
  subheadline="UK premium insurer vs BCBS-affiliated US specialist. Different strengths for different expats."
  tocItems={tocItems}
  relatedLinks={relatedLinks}
  ctaButtonText="Get Quotes from Both"
  ctaButtonHref="/best/expat-health-insurance"
>
  <h2 id="overview">Overview</h2>
  <p>
    BUPA Global and GeoBlue serve different expat markets. BUPA is a premium global insurer available to anyone; GeoBlue specifically serves Americans abroad with BCBS network access.
  </p>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">BUPA Global</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
        <li>Available to all nationalities</li>
        <li>Premium service and support</li>
        <li>Best-in-class mental health</li>
        <li>Strong worldwide network</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">GeoBlue</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
        <li>Designed for US citizens</li>
        <li>BCBS network access in US</li>
        <li>Seamless US-abroad coverage</li>
        <li>US-based customer service</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <CTABox
    title="Compare Both Providers"
    description="Get personalized quotes based on your situation."
    buttonText="Get Free Quotes"
    buttonHref="/best/expat-health-insurance"
    variant="highlight"
  />

  <h2 id="coverage-comparison">Coverage Comparison</h2>
  <p>
    Both provide comprehensive international coverage. BUPA offers more globally, while GeoBlue is optimized for Americans.
  </p>

  <div class="my-8 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
    <ComparisonTable columns={coverageColumns} rows={coverageRows} />
  </div>

  <p><strong>Key differences:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>GeoBlue is primarily for US citizens; BUPA accepts all nationalities</li>
    <li>GeoBlue includes BCBS network access; BUPA charges extra for US coverage</li>
    <li>BUPA has superior mental health coverage and chronic condition support</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="pricing">Pricing</h2>
  <p>
    GeoBlue is often slightly cheaper, especially considering US coverage is included. BUPA's premium pricing reflects its service quality.
  </p>

  <div class="my-8 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
    <ComparisonTable columns={pricingColumns} rows={pricingRows} />
  </div>

  <p><strong>Pricing notes:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>GeoBlue prices include US coverage via BCBS</li>
    <li>BUPA prices exclude US; add 30-40% for US inclusion</li>
    <li>With US coverage added, BUPA is notably more expensive</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="network-and-claims">Network and Claims</h2>

  <h3>Provider Networks</h3>
  <p>
    <strong>BUPA Global</strong> has extensive worldwide direct billing. Strong in Europe, Middle East, and Asia-Pacific.
  </p>
  <p>
    <strong>GeoBlue</strong> provides access to 1.7+ million BCBS providers in the US plus international networks abroad.
  </p>

  <h3>Customer Service</h3>
  <p>
    BUPA is renowned for service quality with dedicated care teams. GeoBlue offers solid US-based support familiar to Americans.
  </p>

  <h2 id="who-should-choose">Who Should Choose Which</h2>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
    <div class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Choose BUPA Global If:</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
        <li>You're not a US citizen</li>
        <li>Mental health coverage is important</li>
        <li>You prioritize service quality</li>
        <li>You don't need regular US care</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Choose GeoBlue If:</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
        <li>You're a US citizen</li>
        <li>You want BCBS network access</li>
        <li>You visit the US regularly</li>
        <li>You prefer US-style service</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 id="verdict">Our Verdict</h2>
  <p>
    For US citizens, GeoBlue offers excellent value with integrated BCBS access—hard to beat for Americans who travel home regularly.
  </p>
  <p>
    For non-US citizens, or Americans who prioritize mental health coverage and premium service over US network access, BUPA Global is worth the higher cost.
  </p>

  <CTABox
    title="Ready to Decide?"
    description="Get quotes based on your citizenship and needs."
    buttonText="Compare Plans Now"
    buttonHref="/best/expat-health-insurance"
    variant="highlight"
  />

  <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6 mt-8">
    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">
      <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> GeoBlue is primarily available to US citizens. Verify eligibility and coverage details with providers.
    </p>
  </div>
</PageShell>
